  "title": "Customer Relations Officer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Resident Engagement:</strong> Act as the main point of contact for residents, addressing inquiries, complaints, and feedback.</li><li><strong>Defects Management:</strong> Monitor and update residents on the status of defect rectifications.</li><li><strong>Appointment Scheduling:</strong> Arrange inspections with the Building Service Centre (BSC) team.</li><li><strong>Liaison Work:</strong> Coordinate with HDB, Town Council, consultants, and subcontractors.</li><li><strong>Administrative Duties:</strong> Prepare reports, manage correspondence, and maintain records.</li><li><strong>Public Relations:</strong> Write notices to inform residents about construction activities.</li><li><strong>Site Coordination:</strong> Work with site supervisors to schedule rectification work.</li><li><strong>Information Centre Management:</strong> Maintain and upkeep the service centre.</li></ul>",
