    "description": "<h3>Our Story</h3>\n<p>Since our founding in 1992, Teambuild Construction Group has transformed into a dynamic, multi-disciplinary powerhouse in the construction industry. Specializing in residential, institutional, and industrial projects, we pride ourselves on our commitment to technical excellence and high safety standards, earning us over 150 prestigious awards.</p>\n<h3>Leading the Way in Innovation</h3>\n<p>Teambuild is at the forefront of construction innovation. As pioneers of Prefabricated Pre-Finished Volumetric Construction (PPVC) in Singapore, we also embrace the latest in IDD and BIM technologies to stay ahead.</p>\n<h3>Investing in Our People</h3>\n<p>Our greatest asset is our talented team of over 1,200 employees. We are committed to nurturing their growth through our Career Mentorship Programme (CMP). This 6-year fast track programme transforms young engineers into Project Managers, providing comprehensive training in both technical and soft skills.</p>\n<h3>Embracing Technology</h3>\n<p>Our passion for technology and innovation ensures we lead the industry in construction excellence. We continuously adopt new advancements to maintain our competitive edge.</p>\n<h3>Be Part of Our Journey</h3>\n<p>At Teambuild Construction Group, we offer more than just a job; we provide a platform for growth and achievement. Experience a dynamic workplace where innovation and excellence thrive. Join us in Building Excellence and Shaping the Future!</p>\n<p><strong>Teambuild Construction Group - Building Excellence, Shaping the Future!</strong></p>",
